reviewText: This collection features four randomly selected episodes from "The Adventures of Ozzie and Harriet" show.  If I were you, I'd wait for the entire series.  It's coming to DVD around December 2014.  Sam Nelson, Ricky Nelson's son, is restoring the entire series.)
I would buy all of the Ozzie and Harriet items if they would list all the episodes that are on each dvd. I'm so tired of duplicating so many that I've seen before.
